( Carnage: I am sorry for spelling Tankorr's name wrong, forgive me.)

* Carnage looked up and nodded as Tankorr stood and fired at her, at least 
she was getting a reaction from him now. Now one in which she approved of 
but one in which was expected.
Carnage stepped back and snickered as a few of Tankorr's artillery fell 
short of her, it felt good to be in battle again!
She then looked up and was suddenly blown backwards as the remainder of his 
weapons hit her head on, she handed on her back a few feet from her original 
spot...slightly damaged.
Carnage then flipped to her feet and glared at the Predacon general, now it 
was her turn!
She drew a charge pistol from her back compartment and fired immediately 
upon the Predacon, now the real fun began!*
